Kingsway Financial plans issue , split . Kingsway Financial Services Inc said on Tuesday it signed an agreement with underwriters for a public offering of C $ 30 million worth of common shares . This offering will be accompanied by a concurrent secondary issue of up to C $ 6 million by Intercargo Corp , Kingsway ' s largest shareholder . Kingsway said proceeds will be used to increase the regulatory capital for some of its insurance operations , for working capital and for future strategic acquisitions . The company also said its board passed a resolution to subdivide the company ' s stock on a two - for - one basis . 
